title: Tianhao Cao
text:
Hello! I am a student at the University of British Columbia (UBC), passionate about bridging the gap between Statistics and Computer Science.
My primary interests lie in Data Science, Machine Learning, and Natural Language Processing (NLP). I enjoy building tools that solve real-world problems—whether it’s analyzing text data or configuring hardware interfaces.

Education
University of British Columbia | Vancouver, BC Undergraduate Student in Statistics & Computer Science | Sept 2022 - Present

Data Science: Machine Learning, NLP (Word Embeddings, Parsing)
Other: Music Theory, Mathematics
